@NODE "CREANAM" "Creature Name"

    The name of the creature such as: Skeleton.  Names can be whatever you
    wish however you are limited to 16 characters.
    
    @{b}NOTE: ENTERING THE CREATURE NAME CREATES THE CREATURE.  IF YOU DO
          NOT ENTER A NAME, NONE OF YOUR CHANGES WILL BE SAVED.@{ub}

