@NODE "CREATYPE" "Creature Type"

    This specifies wether the creature is hostile towards the @{"PC's" link GLOB 3} or
    friendly
    
@ENDNODE

@NODE "CREAHIT" "Hit Points"

This specifies how many hit points the creature has.  See @{"Hit Points" link GLOB 5} for
