@ENDNODE

@NODE "EPLEV" "Exp Pts/Level"

    This is number of experience points the @{"PC" link GLOB} has to gain before he/she can
    go up a level.  Going up a level increases attributes and hit points.
    
@ENDNODE

@NODE "HPADD" "Hit Pts Added"

